              <fr:mainmatter>
                <html:p>A type <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[A]]></fr:tex> is said to be a <html:em><html:strong>proposition</html:strong></html:em> when every <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[x:A]]></fr:tex>, the type <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[A]]></fr:tex> is <fr:link href="foreign-erct-erct-001H.xml" title="Contractible type" addr="forest://erct/erct-001H" type="local">contractible with centre</fr:link> <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[x]]></fr:tex>, i.e. all elements of <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[A]]></fr:tex> are identified.</html:p>
